{"tid":1671370,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[提提大家系列] 加泰人權集會 和 全港連濃牆","createTime":"2019-10-23T12:29:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T10:01:36.000Z","uid":94771,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ee36c27dadd10e498acc1512faa8b50d5407bc15","tid":1671370,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T12:29:10.000Z","msg":"<strong>明天</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zBGq4bu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzBGq4bu.jpg&h=3c5d3e3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>另外還有</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KErytDd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKErytDd.jpg&h=9efef0c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n［提提大家系列］，一視同仁<br />\n明白有活動十分有爭議，我自己都十五十六，但我覺得要尊重其他同路人意見<br />\n所以唔會因為有爭議就唔開行動ＰＯＳＴ推個個活動<br />\n<br />\n認同的推，唔認同的不推　<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。　推定唔推自己選擇<br />\n<br />\n同場加映<br />\n<strong>星期五</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cO4DELr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcO4DELr.jpg&h=e00197b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>光復十點大叫</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jGLrODR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjGLrODR.jpg&h=a3419d47&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6485263dcc00fbf83f3c25414eec8fcf32e20ef5","tid":1671370,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T12:30:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1665303/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1665303/page/1</a><br />\n[文宣升級] 郵差叔叔送信純熟將文宣迅速送出!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4H03stW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4H03stW.png&h=37a4782b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2DEDEJe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2DEDEJe.jpg&h=07